  <description><![CDATA[<p>At Hotel Hammerhof you'll blend seamlessly into a quiet <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austrian</a> way of life. Set slightly aback from the main village it enjoys a tranquil position at the foot of the Bischofmütze Mountain. The onsite farm, and friendly welcome from the Ebner family add to the merry atmosphere here.</p>
<h2>Homely hotel</h2>
<p>The former 400-year-old farm has been renovated into a charming hotel run by the Ebner family. There's still an organic farm attached to the hotel, almost all products made on the farm are served on the tasty breakfast buffet. </p>
<p>The Hammerhof has a traditional Austrian feel to it, whether you are enjoying a drink in the cosy stube bar or relaxing in your bedroom, you'll feel right at home.  And with a backdrop of the incredible Salzburg mountains, the views truly are picture perfect. </p>
<h2>Leisure facilities</h2>
<p>On the lower levels, you'll find a lovely little wellness area complete with a sauna, steam bath, solarium and herbal bath. If you still have energy to burn there is also a fitness room available for you to use.  After a day on the slopes make the most of the games room with table football, pool table and table tennis.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Hammerhof making us the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
